{"tid":973596,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭否認放寬樓宇按揭成數，好友打咗兩日飛機要休息吓","createTime":"2019-01-08T09:38:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-08T17:15:51.000Z","uid":22839,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"06a015373896c55f0ca6637f33f054c1687d5743","tid":973596,"uid":22839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T09:38:12.000Z","msg":"財政司司長陳茂波日前出席電台節目時表示，留意到市民有能力供樓，但未能承擔首期的情況，稱適當時候會調整按揭成數限制，翌日更在網誌表示政府研究為有能力供款但首期不足的上車客，尋求解決方案「並非不可考慮」。財爺考慮出手的消息發酵了兩天，特首林鄭月娥周二卻「潑冷水」，重申現未有即時計劃放寬樓宇按揭成數，指現時放寬按揭只會令巿民供樓的負擔更大，又說根據數字，私樓樓價去年8月至11月底錄得下跌，但去年全年整體樓價仍上升，且幅度不少，故一定「不撤辣、不減辣」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190108/59118478\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190108%2F59118478&d=4Ag1gy5rOgZ5EjT6Eq90HAtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=2017e68a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190108%2F59118478&h=5c814ed0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190108/59118478</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">呢兩日啲剛需又可以縮返埋入老母個西度下次先扲出嚟用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></strong>"},{"pid":"635f74f1b7425dd2b9c8b9b602d9bc8d79aa9ca7","tid":973596,"uid":150378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T09:39:28.000Z","msg":"呃D傻仔去買樓托住個市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b722a022b9ea1c54358b7aa7938a4bd7afa2f7e1","tid":973596,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T09:47:33.000Z","msg":"即係陳茂波想先斬後奏？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b112923094828e79f21635c449978c4c9eb797f","tid":973596,"uid":15711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T17:15:51.000Z","msg":"大巴大巴 ，睇